Action parameter of a waypoint action. There are two situation where the action parameter value will be important. First, when the time to stay at a waypoint is set and when a part of the aircraft or the entire aircraft needs to be rotated. In that case, the action parameter will be the angle of rotation. For waypoint actions where there are no rotations involved or the aircraft is not being asked to stay at a certain location for a set amount of time, the action parameter of a waypoint action will be ignored.
